s3Items.name: HP Printer logs Data
s3Items.description: AWS S3 location for HP Printer logs folder, from all geos and is partitioned by event date. These are brought in with privacy-preserving, and are AES-256 encrypted symmetrically. Also archived to glacier every 30d.
